<p><b>The complete foundry. In-house pattern shop; Green sand &amp; silica no-bake molding; 3d printing &amp; rapid prototyping; machining, finishing &amp; assembly services; From concepts to finish parts.<br></b></p>
<p>Established in 1963 by journeyman pattern maker Wally Thompson, for over half-a-century TF has been dedicated to providing quality casting services to clients from all over the world. Evolving with time, TF has continued to grow &amp; diversify, offering effective solutions for common manufacturing challenges - Rapid prototyping, accommodating small &amp; large production runs, part improvements &amp; customization.</p>
